# Placeholder for Power BI Project

This folder will contain your Power BI project files when you add them.

## Expected Structure:

```
Contoso 10k.SemanticModel/
├── definition/
│   ├── database.tmdl
│   ├── model.tmdl
│   ├── tables/
│   ├── relationships/
│   └── ...
└── .pbi/
```

## How to Add Your Project:

1. Download the Contoso sample data from:
   https://github.com/sql-bi/Contoso-Data-Generator-V2-Data/releases/download/ready-to-use-data/pbix-10k.7z

2. Open the .pbix file in Power BI Desktop

3. Save it as a .pbip file in the root of this repository

4. The folder structure will be created automatically

5. Commit and push your changes
